1
00:01:49,250 --> 00:01:52,583
♪

2
00:01:58,291 --> 00:02:00,666
[gasping]

3
00:02:27,500 --> 00:02:28,791
[gasps]

4
00:02:32,375 --> 00:02:34,916
[guffawing]

5
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:37,291
The great sorcerer Koenig
is here.

6
00:02:37,375 --> 00:02:39,708
I hope you don't mind
my dropping in.

7
00:02:39,791 --> 00:02:41,583
Leon.

8
00:02:41,666 --> 00:02:45,250
I'll defeat you and claim
my place as the Demon Lord.

9
00:02:45,333 --> 00:02:47,291
It's time
for you to die, pretender!

10
00:02:48,458 --> 00:02:50,083
I see.

11
00:02:50,166 --> 00:02:51,916
While that does sound amusing,

12
00:02:52,875 --> 00:02:54,666
I believe I'll pass.

13
00:02:55,666 --> 00:02:57,458
-Take care of him, Ifrit.
-[gasping]

14
00:02:58,958 --> 00:03:00,291
[LEON]
What's wrong?

15
00:03:01,875 --> 00:03:03,583
[shudders]

16
00:03:03,666 --> 00:03:05,333
[yelling]

17
00:03:05,416 --> 00:03:08,083
You can't just ignore me, Leon,
I will have my fight with you!

18
00:03:10,958 --> 00:03:13,500
How cute, the child
has a death wish.

19
00:03:13,583 --> 00:03:16,708
Very well then.
I'm happy to oblige!

20
00:03:16,791 --> 00:03:19,541
♪

21
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,208
[KOENIG gasps]

22
00:03:26,375 --> 00:03:28,958
[screaming]

23
00:03:33,541 --> 00:03:35,125
[chuckles]

24
00:03:35,208 --> 00:03:36,916
That was quite impressive.

25
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,458
Huh?

26
00:03:39,541 --> 00:03:42,416
[LEON] Tell me, child.
What's your name?

27
00:03:43,875 --> 00:03:45,958
Shizue.

28
00:03:46,041 --> 00:03:48,500
Shizu. Eh?

29
00:03:48,583 --> 00:03:50,250
Hmm.

30
00:03:50,333 --> 00:03:52,666
As of today,
you'll be called Shizu.

31
00:03:53,750 --> 00:03:55,583
[SHIZU]
Shizu?

32
00:03:55,666 --> 00:03:56,791
[barks]

33
00:03:56,875 --> 00:03:58,041
Uh...

34
00:04:04,083 --> 00:04:05,291
[chuckles]

35
00:04:05,375 --> 00:04:07,416
You can eat
all you want, okay?

36
00:04:08,833 --> 00:04:10,125
-[twig snaps]
-Huh?

37
00:04:10,208 --> 00:04:11,166
[gasps]

38
00:04:13,625 --> 00:04:16,375
[PIRINO] Uh, he got separated
from his mother.

39
00:04:16,458 --> 00:04:18,708
Please don't tell
anyone about this.

40
00:04:20,125 --> 00:04:22,125
It'll be our secret.

41
00:04:22,208 --> 00:04:24,125
Do you think I could
help care for him?

42
00:04:24,208 --> 00:04:26,166
[gasps]

43
00:04:26,250 --> 00:04:28,583
Yes. I'd like that.

44
00:04:31,208 --> 00:04:33,875
Look, he's eating it.

45
00:04:33,958 --> 00:04:34,875
[BOTH giggle]

46
00:04:34,958 --> 00:04:36,125
[chuckles]

47
00:04:36,208 --> 00:04:37,583
He's so cute. What's his name?

48
00:04:37,666 --> 00:04:40,625
Monsters don't
typically have names.

49
00:04:40,708 --> 00:04:43,291
[SHIZU] Well, we have to
call him something.

50
00:04:43,375 --> 00:04:45,416
[whimpers]

51
00:04:45,500 --> 00:04:47,833
It sounds like he agrees.

52
00:04:47,916 --> 00:04:49,333
What about "Pizu"?

53
00:04:49,416 --> 00:04:51,041
Pizu.

54
00:04:51,125 --> 00:04:54,083
That's perfect.
Right, Pizu?

55
00:04:54,166 --> 00:04:55,791
[PIZU whimpers]

56
00:04:55,875 --> 00:04:57,000
[gasps]

57
00:04:57,958 --> 00:05:00,583
Look at that.
He just got bigger!

58
00:05:00,666 --> 00:05:01,833
[laughs]

59
00:05:01,916 --> 00:05:03,875
You're such a good boy.

60
00:05:05,916 --> 00:05:07,500
[SHIZU]
Pirino, you know that you can't

61
00:05:07,583 --> 00:05:09,666
take him into the castle, right?

62
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:12,375
Aw, he'll be okay.
He's really smart.

63
00:05:12,458 --> 00:05:14,000
[SHIZU]
But...

64
00:05:14,083 --> 00:05:16,083
Besides, you've seen
how friendly he is.

65
00:05:16,166 --> 00:05:18,375
I'm sure they'll let him
be my familiar.

66
00:05:18,458 --> 00:05:19,625
[PIZU whimpers]

67
00:05:20,583 --> 00:05:22,125
If you say so.

68
00:05:23,083 --> 00:05:24,791
-[snarling]
-Hey.

69
00:05:24,875 --> 00:05:26,250
Uh, what's wrong with you?

70
00:05:26,333 --> 00:05:29,625
Stop it. Calm down for a second.

71
00:05:29,708 --> 00:05:31,541
-It's okay.
-[snarling continues]

72
00:05:31,625 --> 00:05:34,291
[gasps]
Uh, just be a good boy. Pizu.

73
00:05:34,375 --> 00:05:36,250
[PIRINO gasping]

74
00:05:37,208 --> 00:05:39,791
You're all right.
Everything's fine.

75
00:05:39,875 --> 00:05:41,625
[PIZU snarling]

76
00:05:41,708 --> 00:05:43,000
[PIRINO gasps]

77
00:05:44,125 --> 00:05:45,416
Shizu?

78
00:05:45,500 --> 00:05:47,125
[snarling continues]

79
00:05:48,500 --> 00:05:49,666
A threat.

80
00:05:52,708 --> 00:05:53,958
[PIRINO gasps]

81
00:05:54,041 --> 00:05:56,000
[PIRINO screaming]

82
00:06:00,791 --> 00:06:01,791
[scoffs]

83
00:06:01,875 --> 00:06:03,875
♪

84
00:06:06,833 --> 00:06:09,750
[voice breaking]
What did I just do?

85
00:06:10,708 --> 00:06:13,583
My whole body,

86
00:06:13,666 --> 00:06:16,083
it felt like it was
moving on its own.

87
00:06:16,166 --> 00:06:18,583
And the fire,

88
00:06:18,666 --> 00:06:20,541
it wasn't me.

89
00:06:20,625 --> 00:06:21,958
I couldn't stop!

90
00:06:22,041 --> 00:06:24,416
[crying]

91
00:06:27,666 --> 00:06:29,541
♪

92
00:06:29,625 --> 00:06:30,541
[gasps]

93
00:06:30,625 --> 00:06:32,375
[birds chirping]

94
00:06:32,458 --> 00:06:34,083
[panting]

95
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:45,625
[gasps]

96
00:06:45,708 --> 00:06:48,333
♪

97
00:06:55,250 --> 00:06:56,958
[gasps]

98
00:07:11,625 --> 00:07:14,041
[footsteps approaching]

99
00:07:14,125 --> 00:07:17,166
[RIMURU] Good morning.
Do you like our little village?

100
00:07:21,041 --> 00:07:23,083
Yes. I love it.

101
00:07:23,166 --> 00:07:25,916
[RIMURU chuckles]
Glad to hear it, Shizu.

102
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,958
You're more than welcome
to stay here.

103
00:07:28,041 --> 00:07:32,375
I appreciate it,
but I really should be going.

104
00:07:32,458 --> 00:07:33,666
[RIMURU]
Why's that?

105
00:07:33,750 --> 00:07:35,250
Because if I do stay here,

106
00:07:35,333 --> 00:07:37,250
I'm afraid I'll bring you
nothing but trouble.

107
00:07:37,333 --> 00:07:39,000
[RIMURU]
Huh?

108
00:07:40,958 --> 00:07:43,291
There's still something
that I need to do.

109
00:07:43,375 --> 00:07:44,833
[RIMURU]
Like what?

110
00:07:46,166 --> 00:07:49,666
I'm on a quest to find the man
who summoned me to this world.

111
00:07:51,208 --> 00:07:53,333
[RIMURU]
What happens when you find him?

112
00:07:53,416 --> 00:07:55,208
♪

113
00:08:01,875 --> 00:08:03,333
[RIMURU]
Okay, then.

114
00:08:03,416 --> 00:08:05,583
Just promise that you'll
come back and visit sometime.

115
00:08:05,666 --> 00:08:07,833
You're always welcome here,
right, Ranga?

116
00:08:07,916 --> 00:08:08,833
Yes, of course.

117
00:08:08,916 --> 00:08:11,166
Well, I'll do my best.

118
00:08:14,791 --> 00:08:17,041
-Thank you. I mean it.
-[RANGA whimpers]

119
00:08:18,583 --> 00:08:20,541
♪

120
00:08:25,458 --> 00:08:28,583
Hey, Shizu. Come back with us.
It'll be fun.

121
00:08:28,666 --> 00:08:30,208
[gasps]

122
00:08:30,291 --> 00:08:33,083
[EREN] Honestly, I'm just
not ready to say goodbye yet.

123
00:08:33,166 --> 00:08:36,625
Eren, you're all
exceptional adventurers.

124
00:08:36,708 --> 00:08:38,791
And I have no doubt that
traveling with the three of you

125
00:08:38,875 --> 00:08:40,416
would probably be entertaining.

126
00:08:40,500 --> 00:08:42,041
So, okay?

127
00:08:44,875 --> 00:08:47,125
Joining with you all
has shown me how good it is

128
00:08:47,208 --> 00:08:49,666
to adventure
with a group of friends.

129
00:08:49,750 --> 00:08:51,625
And I want you to know
I'm truly grateful

130
00:08:51,708 --> 00:08:53,708
that my last journey
was with you guys.

131
00:08:53,791 --> 00:08:57,458
Wait, hold on.
What are you trying to say?

132
00:08:57,541 --> 00:09:00,500
I've been around
for a few decades now.

133
00:09:00,583 --> 00:09:03,250
I may look young,
but I'm not.

134
00:09:03,333 --> 00:09:07,041
Oh. I get it, you were just
making a silly joke, huh?

135
00:09:07,125 --> 00:09:09,833
Sheesh, you shouldn't
scare me like that, Shizu.

136
00:09:12,291 --> 00:09:14,208
Ah. Here they come.

137
00:09:14,291 --> 00:09:16,583
Sorry to keep you all waiting.

138
00:09:16,666 --> 00:09:19,000
We've been standing
out here forever.

139
00:09:19,083 --> 00:09:22,666
Yeah. And why do women take
so long to get ready, anyway?

140
00:09:25,125 --> 00:09:26,125
[gasps]

141
00:09:26,208 --> 00:09:28,958
♪

142
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:34,125
Why'd you stop?

143
00:09:35,125 --> 00:09:37,291
[groaning]

144
00:09:37,375 --> 00:09:39,583
Is something the matter, miss?

145
00:09:39,666 --> 00:09:41,625
[SHIZU]
No, not again.

146
00:09:41,708 --> 00:09:44,083
-Uh, hey.
-What's happening to her?

147
00:09:44,166 --> 00:09:45,041
[groans sharply]

148
00:09:45,125 --> 00:09:46,375
Something's not right!

149
00:09:46,458 --> 00:09:48,666
[groaning]

150
00:09:48,750 --> 00:09:51,375
[screaming]

151
00:09:51,458 --> 00:09:54,250
♪

152
00:09:56,833 --> 00:09:59,125
What the heck?
What's wrong, Shizu?

153
00:09:59,208 --> 00:10:00,333
[KAVAL gasps]

154
00:10:00,416 --> 00:10:02,833
♪

155
00:10:12,458 --> 00:10:13,666
[RIMURU gasps]

156
00:10:22,791 --> 00:10:24,708
[ALL grunt, scream]

157
00:10:26,375 --> 00:10:27,708
[RIMURU gasping]

158
00:10:28,666 --> 00:10:30,500
[RIMURU]
Whoa! Is everyone all right?

159
00:10:30,583 --> 00:10:32,166
Okay, what the hell?

160
00:10:32,250 --> 00:10:34,083
We're gonna charge
hazard pay for this.

161
00:10:34,166 --> 00:10:35,958
Yeah, well, tell that
to the guild master

162
00:10:36,041 --> 00:10:37,041
next time you see him.

163
00:10:37,125 --> 00:10:39,375
Look up there! It's Shizu!

164
00:10:42,583 --> 00:10:45,583
Wait. Shizue Izawa?

165
00:10:45,666 --> 00:10:48,041
-[EREN gasps]
-You've gotta be kidding me.

166
00:10:48,125 --> 00:10:50,458
Isn't she the Conqueror
of Flames?

167
00:10:52,500 --> 00:10:53,833
-[RIMURU] Huh?
-[EREN] Hold on!

168
00:10:53,916 --> 00:10:56,041
You mean she's
the legendary hero of the guild

169
00:10:56,125 --> 00:10:57,291
from 50 years ago?

170
00:10:57,375 --> 00:10:59,125
They're the same girl?

171
00:10:59,208 --> 00:11:00,791
Impossible.

172
00:11:00,875 --> 00:11:02,291
How?

173
00:11:02,375 --> 00:11:04,541
All the rumors that
I've heard say she's retired.

174
00:11:08,541 --> 00:11:10,333
-[RIMURU] Rigurd. Rigur.
-[BOTH] Hmm?

175
00:11:10,416 --> 00:11:12,166
[RIMURU]
Evacuate the town.

176
00:11:12,250 --> 00:11:14,916
-Are you sure?
-What about you?

177
00:11:15,000 --> 00:11:16,125
[RIMURU]
That's an order.

178
00:11:16,208 --> 00:11:18,041
Of course, as you wish,
Lord Rimuru.

179
00:11:18,125 --> 00:11:20,041
[BOTH panting]

180
00:11:22,208 --> 00:11:24,041
[RIMURU]
Are you there, Ranga?

181
00:11:24,125 --> 00:11:26,083
[RANGA]
Yes, Master. I'm here.

182
00:11:26,166 --> 00:11:27,458
[RIMURU]
I need you to be ready.

183
00:11:27,541 --> 00:11:28,500
[RANGA]
Right!

184
00:11:34,750 --> 00:11:37,333
♪

185
00:11:47,833 --> 00:11:50,375
[grunting]

186
00:11:52,500 --> 00:11:55,375
That thing is Ifrit.
The fire spirit.

187
00:11:55,458 --> 00:11:57,083
Then there's no doubt about it.

188
00:11:57,166 --> 00:11:58,458
That means Shizu...

189
00:11:58,541 --> 00:12:00,166
Is the fabled hero.

190
00:12:00,250 --> 00:12:02,083
She's the Conqueror of Flames.

191
00:12:02,166 --> 00:12:05,583
Ugh. I'm pretty sure we can't
win against that monster.

192
00:12:05,666 --> 00:12:07,000
Yeah, you're right.

193
00:12:07,083 --> 00:12:09,833
I hate to admit it,
but we're as good as dead.

194
00:12:09,916 --> 00:12:13,625
Well, it may have been short,
but at least it was a good life.

195
00:12:13,708 --> 00:12:14,791
♪

196
00:12:14,875 --> 00:12:16,333
[roaring]

197
00:12:20,791 --> 00:12:22,500
-[grunts]
-[ALL scream]

198
00:12:22,583 --> 00:12:24,458
♪

199
00:12:24,541 --> 00:12:27,000
[RIMURU screams, gasps]

200
00:12:37,083 --> 00:12:40,208
[RIMURU] Yo, what gives?
We just built this town, dammit!

201
00:12:40,291 --> 00:12:42,458
[EREN weakly]
That hurt.

202
00:12:42,541 --> 00:12:44,291
[RIMURU] You guys need
to get out of here.

203
00:12:45,500 --> 00:12:47,625
[KAVAL]
We're not going anywhere.

204
00:12:51,166 --> 00:12:52,250
[RIMURU]
Huh?

205
00:12:52,333 --> 00:12:53,750
I don't know what's going on

206
00:12:53,833 --> 00:12:55,875
or why she's out for blood
all of a sudden.

207
00:12:55,958 --> 00:12:58,166
But she's still
a member of our party.

208
00:12:58,250 --> 00:13:00,041
And we won't abandon her.

209
00:13:00,125 --> 00:13:03,500
[RIMURU]
Okay. Just be careful.

210
00:13:03,583 --> 00:13:05,083
They're really good people.

211
00:13:05,166 --> 00:13:07,916
[KAVAL scoffs] I can't believe
we're about to face off

212
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:10,541
against an actual
legendary hero.

213
00:13:10,625 --> 00:13:13,875
Uh-huh. You never know what life
is gonna throw at you.

214
00:13:15,333 --> 00:13:16,833
[RIMURU]
Let's go.

215
00:13:21,875 --> 00:13:24,625
[RIMURU] Hey, what is it
you want from us?

216
00:13:29,708 --> 00:13:30,958
[RIMURU grunts]

217
00:13:31,041 --> 00:13:32,291
Water blade!

218
00:13:32,375 --> 00:13:34,333
♪

219
00:13:37,625 --> 00:13:39,333
Yeah, I sort of expected that.

220
00:13:39,416 --> 00:13:41,125
-[SALAMANDER screeching]
-[RIMURU gasps]

221
00:13:43,250 --> 00:13:44,541
[gasps]

222
00:13:44,625 --> 00:13:46,416
-[EREN] Icicle lance!
-[RIMURU] Huh?

223
00:13:47,541 --> 00:13:48,708
[screeches]

224
00:13:54,875 --> 00:13:57,375
[RIMURU]
Are you guys doing all right?

225
00:13:57,458 --> 00:13:58,916
We can take care
of these monsters.

226
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:01,166
Putting our lives on the line
and saving others

227
00:14:01,250 --> 00:14:02,750
is just part
of being adventurers.

228
00:14:02,833 --> 00:14:05,333
What did I tell you
about stealing my lines?

229
00:14:05,416 --> 00:14:07,375
The leader is supposed
to say that.

230
00:14:07,458 --> 00:14:09,000
Well, whatever.

231
00:14:09,083 --> 00:14:10,875
Let's show these lizards
who's boss.

232
00:14:10,958 --> 00:14:13,625
If nothing else, we'll at least
take one of them out.

233
00:14:13,708 --> 00:14:15,625
[RIMURU]
I like your confidence,

234
00:14:15,708 --> 00:14:16,875
but be careful anyway.

235
00:14:16,958 --> 00:14:18,333
Whoa!

236
00:14:18,416 --> 00:14:19,833
[screeching]

237
00:14:19,916 --> 00:14:22,500
♪

238
00:14:22,583 --> 00:14:23,916
Ranga!

239
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:25,416
[RANGA]
Right!

240
00:14:25,500 --> 00:14:28,500
♪

241
00:14:31,666 --> 00:14:32,791
[RANGA grunts]

242
00:14:32,875 --> 00:14:34,708
[RIMURU]
Here they come.

243
00:14:38,833 --> 00:14:40,375
[RANGA grunts]

244
00:14:40,458 --> 00:14:42,125
[RIMURU] Just concentrate
on evading them.

245
00:14:42,208 --> 00:14:43,583
I'll handle the attacks.

246
00:14:43,666 --> 00:14:44,833
[RANGA]
As you wish!

247
00:14:44,916 --> 00:14:46,541
♪

248
00:14:52,250 --> 00:14:54,541
[RANGA howling]

249
00:14:54,625 --> 00:14:56,625
♪

250
00:14:59,625 --> 00:15:00,875
[RIMURU grunts]

251
00:15:03,125 --> 00:15:06,333
[RIMURU] We can't take out Ifrit
with those salamanders around.

252
00:15:06,416 --> 00:15:07,500
This sucks!

253
00:15:07,583 --> 00:15:09,666
He can vaporize my water blade.

254
00:15:10,833 --> 00:15:12,208
What'll happen
if I just shoot them

255
00:15:12,291 --> 00:15:14,708
with all the water
I have stored in my stomach?

256
00:15:14,791 --> 00:15:16,000
[GREAT SAGE]
Answer:

257
00:15:16,083 --> 00:15:18,583
Expulsion of all water
is possible.

258
00:15:18,666 --> 00:15:20,166
If it hits the salamander,

259
00:15:20,250 --> 00:15:22,583
it will cause
an explosion of steam.

260
00:15:22,666 --> 00:15:23,708
Take this action?

261
00:15:23,791 --> 00:15:26,208
[RIMURU]
An explosion, huh?

262
00:15:26,291 --> 00:15:28,208
Will that destroy
the salamanders, though?

263
00:15:28,291 --> 00:15:30,458
[GREAT SAGE]
It is possible.

264
00:15:30,541 --> 00:15:32,458
However, the force of the blast

265
00:15:32,541 --> 00:15:34,916
may destroy
the surrounding area, as well.

266
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:37,375
[RIMURU]
That seems counter-productive!

267
00:15:38,541 --> 00:15:39,458
[gasps]

268
00:15:39,541 --> 00:15:41,291
Icicle Lance!

269
00:15:41,375 --> 00:15:43,208
♪

270
00:15:43,291 --> 00:15:45,083
[screeching]

271
00:15:47,666 --> 00:15:50,250
[RIMURU] Why does her attack
seem to be doing damage?

272
00:15:50,333 --> 00:15:53,708
[GREAT SAGE] Magic attacks are
more effective against spirits.

273
00:15:53,791 --> 00:15:55,166
[RIMURU]
Light bulb!

274
00:15:55,250 --> 00:15:57,166
-Ranga.
-[RANGA] Yes.

275
00:16:00,291 --> 00:16:02,875
[RIMURU]
Eren, fire that attack at me!

276
00:16:02,958 --> 00:16:04,375
What?

277
00:16:04,458 --> 00:16:06,750
No, I'm not gonna attack you,
that would be crazy.

278
00:16:06,833 --> 00:16:08,833
[RIMURU]
Less talking and more shooting!

279
00:16:08,916 --> 00:16:11,125
[EREN] Okay, prepare for
a face full of ice.

280
00:16:11,208 --> 00:16:15,583
Icicle Lance, go!

281
00:16:22,833 --> 00:16:25,500
Impossible!
He slurped up my ice spear?

282
00:16:25,583 --> 00:16:27,166
[GREAT SAGE]
Notice.

283
00:16:27,250 --> 00:16:30,000
Analysis of Icicle Lance
has been completed.

284
00:16:30,083 --> 00:16:31,250
[RIMURU]
Okay!

285
00:16:31,333 --> 00:16:32,875
♪

286
00:16:47,083 --> 00:16:48,458
Icicle Shotgun!

287
00:16:51,875 --> 00:16:53,083
Oh, yeah!

288
00:16:56,541 --> 00:16:58,125
[screeching]

289
00:16:59,666 --> 00:17:01,750
[RIMURU]
Only one left. Huh?

290
00:17:05,333 --> 00:17:07,500
-[KAVAL] Oh, crap.
-[GIDO] It's gonna blow!

291
00:17:07,583 --> 00:17:09,458
♪

292
00:17:11,500 --> 00:17:12,750
[screams]

293
00:17:16,958 --> 00:17:18,333
[RIMURU]
You guys all right?

294
00:17:19,333 --> 00:17:20,750
That's not good.

295
00:17:20,833 --> 00:17:22,750
[groaning quietly]

296
00:17:24,916 --> 00:17:27,375
[RIMURU] Ranga, take them
and go somewhere safe.

297
00:17:27,458 --> 00:17:29,750
-[RANGA] But, Master--
-[RIMURU] Go!

298
00:17:29,833 --> 00:17:31,958
[RANGA]
Right. As you command.

299
00:17:32,041 --> 00:17:33,125
Be careful.

300
00:17:33,208 --> 00:17:34,875
[RIMURU]
Don't worry.

301
00:17:36,916 --> 00:17:38,416
Ifrit is mine.

302
00:17:50,833 --> 00:17:52,166
[RIMURU]
Now then,

303
00:17:52,250 --> 00:17:54,958
we can finally fight
without holding back.

304
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:04,958
[RIMURU gasps]

305
00:18:05,041 --> 00:18:07,833
♪

306
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:19,291
[gasps]

307
00:18:22,291 --> 00:18:24,791
[RIMURU]
Take this! Icicle Shotgun!

308
00:18:32,666 --> 00:18:34,041
It worked!

309
00:18:34,125 --> 00:18:35,208
[gasps]

310
00:18:39,125 --> 00:18:41,458
[roaring]

311
00:18:49,375 --> 00:18:50,375
[RANGA]
Master.

312
00:18:50,458 --> 00:18:52,833
♪

313
00:19:01,125 --> 00:19:03,625
[RIMURU screaming]

314
00:19:05,416 --> 00:19:06,583
[RIMURU]
Why did I just sit there

315
00:19:06,666 --> 00:19:08,625
while he turned up
the heat like that?!

316
00:19:08,708 --> 00:19:10,416
I can't believe
I'm really gonna go out

317
00:19:10,500 --> 00:19:12,041
like a pot of
overcooked pudding!

318
00:19:12,125 --> 00:19:14,791
I just had to get fancy
with the ice moves

319
00:19:14,875 --> 00:19:16,333
when I should have
just demolished this dude

320
00:19:16,416 --> 00:19:17,833
with my Black Lightning!

321
00:19:17,916 --> 00:19:19,666
Figures that right as I was
getting used

322
00:19:19,750 --> 00:19:20,916
to my life as a slime,

323
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:23,500
I'd go and get
myself incinerated again!

324
00:19:24,708 --> 00:19:26,291
It was a short life.

325
00:19:26,375 --> 00:19:28,458
Or "slife." Whatever.

326
00:19:30,625 --> 00:19:34,666
Weird, but I actually don't feel
like I'm taking much damage.

327
00:19:34,750 --> 00:19:38,375
Why is this taking so long,
is Ifrit some kinda tease?

328
00:19:38,458 --> 00:19:40,083
[GREAT SAGE]
Answer:

329
00:19:40,166 --> 00:19:42,583
Due to
Thermal Fluctuation Resistance,

330
00:19:42,666 --> 00:19:44,708
fire attacks are being
automatically nullified

331
00:19:44,791 --> 00:19:45,750
and do not affect you.

332
00:19:45,833 --> 00:19:47,250
[RIMURU]
Ah.

333
00:19:47,333 --> 00:19:48,791
[GREAT SAGE]
Mm-hmm.

334
00:19:48,875 --> 00:19:51,000
[RIMURU]
Why do you sound exasperated?!

335
00:19:51,083 --> 00:19:55,291
Anyway, if I'm immune to
Ifrit's fire attacks, then...

336
00:19:55,375 --> 00:19:57,250
We're playing on easy mode!

337
00:19:57,333 --> 00:19:59,291
It's all good!

338
00:19:59,375 --> 00:20:01,125
No, it's better than good.

339
00:20:01,208 --> 00:20:03,250
It's freaking awesome!

340
00:20:03,333 --> 00:20:06,375
♪

341
00:20:12,958 --> 00:20:13,958
[grunts]

342
00:20:14,041 --> 00:20:15,125
Hmm.

343
00:20:20,625 --> 00:20:21,541
[gasps]

344
00:20:21,625 --> 00:20:22,541
Hmm.

345
00:20:27,291 --> 00:20:29,333
[RIMURU]
Oh, I think I felt an itch.

346
00:20:29,416 --> 00:20:31,041
[grunting]

347
00:20:33,333 --> 00:20:34,666
[gasps]

348
00:20:35,666 --> 00:20:37,625
[RIMURU]
I may have underestimated you,

349
00:20:37,708 --> 00:20:41,000
but not as much as you
underestimated me.

350
00:20:41,083 --> 00:20:43,250
♪

351
00:20:45,583 --> 00:20:47,458
Now it's my turn.

352
00:20:47,541 --> 00:20:49,666
[grunting]

353
00:20:50,666 --> 00:20:51,791
[GREAT SAGE]
Would you like to use

354
00:20:51,875 --> 00:20:54,208
the Unique Skill, Predator?

355
00:20:54,291 --> 00:20:55,583
[RIMURU]
Yes.

356
00:21:04,333 --> 00:21:06,000
[fire crackling]

357
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:13,416
[gasps]
Shizu!

358
00:21:15,125 --> 00:21:16,708
[water gurgling]

359
00:21:25,166 --> 00:21:27,541
Hmm. Hmm.

360
00:21:35,541 --> 00:21:38,041
[MALE VOICE] You might as well
give up, Ifrit.

361
00:21:38,125 --> 00:21:40,625
♪

362
00:21:40,708 --> 00:21:42,208
[gasps]

363
00:21:46,500 --> 00:21:50,083
[MALE VOICE] It is impossible
to break out of this place.

364
00:21:50,166 --> 00:21:52,500
[gasps sharply]

365
00:21:53,625 --> 00:21:56,375
[MALE VOICE]
You are no match for Rimuru.

366
00:21:56,458 --> 00:21:58,833
He is my sworn friend.

367
00:22:01,625 --> 00:22:03,916
I am the Storm Dragon,

368
00:22:04,000 --> 00:22:05,916
Veldora Tempest.

369
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:08,791
And it would be
my pleasure to face you.

370
00:22:08,875 --> 00:22:11,416
[VELDORA laughing menacingly]

371
00:22:16,500 --> 00:22:17,833
[laughter continues]

372
00:23:52,750 --> 00:23:55,333
[GREAT SAGE]
Next time, "Inherited Will."

